name: Push The Ghost - Brains
description:
Second EP from the east coast punks, full of more summer anthems and sing-a-longs!

*Limited Edition* Yellow coloured CD cover for first 100!

1. Brains
2. Keep The Youth In Music
3. Family Tree (30 Second Circle Pit)
4. DIY or Die in GY
5. No One Dances To Push The Ghost

name: Push The Ghost - Listen Up!
description:
7 great punk rock tracks for fans of H20, Bouncing Souls and As Friends Rust. Sing-a-longs guaranteed!

Limited to only 250 copies in cardboard cases

1. Listen Up 
2. Fresh Cuts 
3. blindfaithinyourleaderswillgetyoukilled 
4. Roots 
5. Sucker 
6. FNFG 
7. When I Get To The Club

[sm004] [02/03/2009]

name: The Departed - This Is What We Know
description:
Long awaited and anticipated full length from these hardcore heavy weights! 10 tracks of blistering riffs and brutal beat downs in the vein of Champion, Come Back Kid, Bane and The Legacy! (first 250 copies in limited cardboard cases)

1. Introduction 
2. I Thought You Said Global Welfare Not Warfare 
3. So Long And Thanks For All The Chemicals 
4. Talk Talk Talk 
5. Welcome Home 
6. So Much For Role Models 
7. Find Religion, Forget Free Thought 
8. Every Breath 
9. Skeletons 
10. No Turning Back 

[sm003] [02/03/2009]
